{"tid":1326094,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西自古以來就係我國不可分割嘅一部份","createTime":"2019-07-17T05:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T05:47:38.000Z","uid":234509,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4001568fa760307218b7dbf067be5c9cad9c9410","tid":1326094,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:49:31.000Z","msg":"巴西郡，中國古代政區名。<br />\n<br />\n巴西郡，是東漢末年至隋朝期間，在中國今天四川和重慶地區的一個郡級行政區劃，巴西意為&quot;巴郡以西&quot;，與同時期的巴郡、巴東郡合稱&quot;三巴&quot;，但實際上巴西郡位置大致在巴郡以北，巴東郡以西。<br />\n<br />\n在四川的腹地裏有著這樣一座規模不小的古城，這就是中國四大古城之一閬中--當年張飛鎮守的巴西郡的治所。歲月滄桑，嘉陵江滔滔，繞城而過。物是人非，古城依舊。<br />\n<br />\n中文名稱<br />\n巴西郡<br />\n性質<br />\n中國古代政區名<br />\n時代<br />\n東漢末年至隋朝期間<br />\n位置<br />\n在中國今天四川和重慶地區<br />\n建郡時間<br />\n漢獻帝建安六年（公元201）<br />\n郡治<br />\n閬中縣<br />\n<br />\n班巴閪兵只係回歸祖國嘅懷抱唔係入籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2510ee7df9f954f30aeb158270e6f8330c376b6d","tid":1326094,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"佢地全都是新亭侯征虜將軍巴西太守張飛後裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.guoxue123.com/other/map/pic/06/11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guoxue123.com%2Fother%2Fmap%2Fpic%2F06%2F11.jpg&h=1a3abbf8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29936cfedfdf966883ee4c2723e9503b975a36d5","tid":1326094,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"一起森巴舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1e78be5420c8657576d97c9c659e2461327aad","tid":1326094,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:00:38.000Z","msg":"我咩國<br />\n鄰國ok？"},{"pid":"533e462ca76f0c067964e5f2d469092e9c7828ba","tid":1326094,"uid":50196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2trh3E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb